text:
If you want to get through this process quickly and efficiently...NCH is the way to go. They are very systematic in making sure everything is done properly to avoid delays, fines, penalties, etc.
The whole team (Josh, Kelsey, Tanya, & Chirstine) were all super helpful and always ready to answer any questions that came up along the way.
